{"tid":2347433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【除夕】睇TVB定睇日本橫濱1:1 高達開Live陪你倒數？","createTime":"2020-12-31T04:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T15:42:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb40dae2dd7c03582078042958403afd133ce1b","tid":2347433,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:50:30.000Z","msg":"以前一到聖誕、除夕，好多香港人都選擇去旅行慶祝。不過今年冇得飛，全世界又因為疫情影響都冇乜活動，唔少明星都選擇用直播嘅方式倒數。不過除咗藝人之外，今年要開住live倒數嘅竟然仲有一部1:1高達！<br />\n<br />\n高達官方Youtube Channel ガンダムチャンネル （Gundam Channel）會喺今日香港時間晚上九點開始進行Live除夕特別節目。 仲請咗阪口大助（《機動戰士V高達》胡索聲優），加隈亜衣（《高達創戰潛行者Re:RISE》Freddie聲優），同埋出名喺高達迷嘅聲優綾見有紀呢三位特別嘉賓一齊過新年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nMium155aO4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnMium155aO4&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=bf9aa184\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nMium155aO4</a><br />\n<br />\n橫濱呢個1:1比例大型高達相信唔少人都去過當地朝聖，而今晚嘅live都會同背後嘅製作團隊 GUNDAM FACTORY YOKOHAMA 連線傾計，聽講仲會有 1:1 高達嘅特別表演！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=hobby&amp;aid=25623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fmobile%2Farticle%2Farticle.php%3Fcat%3Dhobby%26aid%3D25623&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=ae68e3bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=hobby&amp;aid=25623</a><br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：tvb <br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 高達"},{"pid":"fde36ff4884579af1a08173c514f6a24e4149731","tid":2347433,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tvb.png?fit=1200%2C650&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2